    v_wind : numpy.ndarray[dtype=float32]
        1D NumPy array of v-wind components (m/s)

    Returns 
    -------
    tuple[nwsspc.sharp.calc.winds.WindComponents, nwsspc.sharp.calc.winds.WindComponents]
        (upshear, downshear)
    """

